{"tid":648101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"辣跑港島半山瘋狂飆車　Cut雙白線　亂爬救護車頭","createTime":"2018-04-30T11:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T17:15:06.000Z","uid":55628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f5cb226eae30711c177862ef4538f1c9d1f29b52","tid":648101,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180430/photo/bkn-20180430113845171-0430_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180430185423\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180430%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180430113845171-0430_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180430185423&h=e98635b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n清晨「飛車」隨時成為馬路炸彈！網民發現連串有在港島區飛車短片上載到互聯網，據「車cam」片的資料，都在昨日(29日)清晨發生，多輛「辣跑」在馬路上風馳電掣，上斜不減速，在雙白線上「頭搖右尾擺」，險象環生。<br />\n<br />\n東網讀者提供多段短片，質疑片中的車輛都懷疑是非法賽車，全部以高速行駛，還明目張膽將「車cam」片放上網分享。根據所有「車cam」片，左下角均顯示4月29日清晨大約5至6時，片段顯示不同款色型號的跑車，於港島半山區瘋狂飛車。<br />\n<br />\n拍攝有關「車cam」片段的跑車飛馳上斜坡期間，切線避開一輛正閃燈的救護車，無視地上雙白線，再「爬頭」駛回救護車前方行車線。相反方向有車駛近則視若無睹。上到半山更無視分隔來自相反方向車輛的雙白線，左搖右擺。飛車的人覺得暢快，但其他駕駛人士就看得膽顫心驚。<br />\n<br />\n[url][<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180430/bkn-20180430113845171-0430_00822_001.html?refer=hn2/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180430%2Fbkn-20180430113845171-0430_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn2%2Furl%5D&d=8wzt19psbD7LDmiXDxLXkwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=e96c2c5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180430/bkn-20180430113845171-0430_00822_001.html?refer=hn2/url]</a>"},{"pid":"f790d311291bb76a760c4c87f4231444c86a9b53","tid":648101,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:39:17.000Z","msg":"有錢就大撚曬架啦<br />\n第一日做地球人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab93ba395d8280f97ab37db33ce071ba9bd38ab8","tid":648101,"uid":163758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T12:50:08.000Z","msg":"香港一單半單就上哂新聞, 我日日都見台狗做同一件事"},{"pid":"c2f1dba6905dee441497a34be3e1e584bfc1240c","tid":648101,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:11:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f03e586f1598f26c3992c9178b969cf00b35ec36","tid":648101,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c2f1dba6905dee441497a34be3e1e584bfc1240c","tid":648101,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:11:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:18:33.000Z","msg":"通常都係富二代...真係有錢佬on9都唔會玩救護車"},{"pid":"ec8093363b2fb85acd63651a90af83f6c7df3e29","tid":648101,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f03e586f1598f26c3992c9178b969cf00b35ec36","tid":648101,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c2f1dba6905dee441497a34be3e1e584bfc1240c","tid":648101,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:11:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:18:33.000Z","msg":"通常都係富二代...真係有錢佬on9都唔會玩救護車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:42:47.000Z","msg":"富三代有可能啲 重要唔係大仔嗰啲<br />\n唔使諗承繼公司 又有錢"},{"pid":"dfdd3659a32f56ebb44fd8ebae4c3406fb73c817","tid":648101,"uid":19287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:50:29.000Z","msg":"白色個架做咩玩玩下唔玩"},{"pid":"f3bf0b8bea0f220cc53a2e06a64f89468dcd9621","tid":648101,"uid":33694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfdd3659a32f56ebb44fd8ebae4c3406fb73c817","tid":648101,"uid":19287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:50:29.000Z","msg":"白色個架做咩玩玩下唔玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:41:07.000Z","msg":"廢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4713716105d1bd4a2abc12fc15efd3e11f9b1ba","tid":648101,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3bf0b8bea0f220cc53a2e06a64f89468dcd9621","tid":648101,"uid":33694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{